Though we’re miles away, our hearts are with our brothers and sisters at home. It’s all we’ve been talking about honestly. All we have are the social media updates and we’re equally anxious and hoping for the best. Thank you so much for playing your part in ensuring our future is better than the present. Thank you to everyone who took the pains to get their PVC, everyone who voted, thank you honestly for playing your part! We’re praying for a new Nigeria and we believe the one who seats on the throne will take the wheels! God bless Nigeria
With love, @mide_wey & I
Thank you @blessedafriqueboutique for this beautiful neck piece that came in so handy when we decided to do this shoot! My interpretation of it is “for God is with her, she will NOT fail”
God is with us, He’s within us and He will take the wheels!
“He will frustrate the devices of the crafty, so that their hands cannot carry out their plans.”
Job 5:12, Amen.
Love you family members.
📸 @mide_wey
